  <brief_title>The Use of Propranolol for the Prevention of Worsening of Esophageal Varices in Patients With Isolated Gastric Varices</brief_title>
  <official_title>Post-balloon Occluded Retrograde Transvenous Obliteration Use of Propranolol for the Prevention of Worsening of Esophageal Varices in Patients With Isolated Gastric Varices</official_title>
